2
00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:17.770
Ace! Luffy!

3
00:00:18.580 --> 00:00:21.980
We gotta set out to sea someday!

4
00:00:21.980 --> 00:00:24.640
Let's get out of this country and live freely!

5
00:00:26.770 --> 00:00:28.650
Starting today...

6
00:00:29.510 --> 00:00:31.310
we're brothers!

7
00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:34.290
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

8
00:00:53.040 --> 00:00:55.130
How long are you gonna keep moping?

9
00:00:58.100 --> 00:01:02.570
All the treasure we hid
in the midway forest is gone.

10
00:01:02.570 --> 00:01:06.410
But that pile of loot doesn't matter anymore.

11
00:01:06.410 --> 00:01:11.730
That was the pirate fund
Sabo and I were gonna use...

12
00:01:11.730 --> 00:01:15.300
But in the end, Sabo didn't need it.

13
00:01:15.300 --> 00:01:19.380
So I'll just let it go, too.

14
00:01:19.380 --> 00:01:23.290
There's no point in gathering
treasure you can't even protect.

15
00:01:23.290 --> 00:01:25.450
A-Ace...

16
00:01:25.450 --> 00:01:26.270
I...

17
00:01:29.140 --> 00:01:31.440
I wanna get stronger!

18
00:01:32.510 --> 00:01:33.760
And stronger...

19
00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:35.280
and stronger...!

20
00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:37.310
Stronger and stronger!

21
00:01:37.310 --> 00:01:38.990
Lots stronger!

22
00:01:38.990 --> 00:01:40.130
Stronger!

23
00:01:40.130 --> 00:01:42.080
Lots and lots stronger!

24
00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:43.880
Stronger and stronger!

25
00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:45.660
So much stronger!

26
00:01:45.660 --> 00:01:47.620
And stronger and stronger!

27
00:01:47.620 --> 00:01:50.020
And even stronger than that!

28
00:01:50.020 --> 00:01:53.390
And then, I'll be able to protect anything.

29
00:01:53.390 --> 00:01:55.590
I won't have to lose anyone ever again!

30
00:01:57.270 --> 00:01:59.740
So please...

31
00:01:59.740 --> 00:02:04.080
Ace, please don't die!

32
00:02:04.080 --> 00:02:06.110
Don't be ridiculous!

33
00:02:06.110 --> 00:02:08.890
Worry about yourself first!

34
00:02:08.890 --> 00:02:10.980
You're way weaker than me!

35
00:02:11.260 --> 00:02:14.220
Listen up, and remember this, Luffy!

36
00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:16.620
I'm not gonna die!

37
00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:20.810
Uh-huh.

38
00:02:21.660 --> 00:02:24.240
Sabo made that request, too.

39
00:02:25.160 --> 00:02:28.360
I promise. There's no way I'll die!

40
00:02:29.300 --> 00:02:32.620
How could I die and leave my
wimpy little brother behind?

41
00:02:33.270 --> 00:02:35.570
Uh-huh... Uh-huh!

42
00:02:35.570 --> 00:02:42.040
I'm not that smart so I don't know
what even killed Sabo.

43
00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:46.460
But... it must've been
the opposite of freedom.

44
00:02:46.900 --> 00:02:50.610
Sabo died without tasting freedom.

45
00:02:50.610 --> 00:02:54.130
But we shared the same cup of sake
with Sabo, and we're still alive!

46
00:02:57.960 --> 00:03:00.870
So, listen up, Luffy.

47
00:03:00.870 --> 00:03:05.700
We have to live our lives without regrets!

48
00:03:05.700 --> 00:03:07.200
Uh-huh.

49
00:03:20.240 --> 00:03:22.540
Noble-born boys...

50
00:03:22.540 --> 00:03:26.150
become true noblemen
on their eighteenth birthday.

51
00:03:27.190 --> 00:03:31.220
That's why I need to leave this country
by the time I turn seventeen!

52
00:03:33.880 --> 00:03:38.520
Someday, we'll head out to sea...

53
00:03:39.100 --> 00:03:41.210
and live however we want!

54
00:03:41.210 --> 00:03:43.420
We'll be more free than anyone!

55
00:03:43.420 --> 00:03:44.260
Uh-huh!

56
00:03:46.140 --> 00:03:51.050
I'm sure we'll make lots
of enemies because of that.

57
00:03:51.050 --> 00:03:55.080
Even Grandpa will be against us.
We'll be risking our lives.

58
00:03:55.910 --> 00:03:58.390
We set sail at seventeen!

59
00:03:58.390 --> 00:04:00.190
And then...

60
00:04:00.190 --> 00:04:01.620
we will become pirates!

61
00:04:42.850 --> 00:04:46.980
Setting out before the day breaks

62
00:04:46.690 --> 00:04:51.490
To greet an unknown tomorrow

63
00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:55.070
We have no regrets in our resolve

64
00:04:54.870 --> 00:04:58.160
(Oh, I know what I’m supposed to do)

65
00:04:57.830 --> 00:05:01.830
No matter what kind of trials lie ahead,

66
00:05:01.500 --> 00:05:06.430
Nothing can stop my throbbing heart

67
00:05:06.040 --> 00:05:11.130
There is only one place to go

68
00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:13.040
(Fly to the light)

69
00:05:12.590 --> 00:05:16.760
Bonds forged through battle

70
00:05:16.390 --> 00:05:20.470
I won’t let anyone get hurt

71
00:05:20.060 --> 00:05:23.270
When I open my clenched fist,

72
00:05:22.850 --> 00:05:26.520
I will find power there

73
00:05:26.190 --> 00:05:28.900
So let’s start

74
00:05:28.570 --> 00:05:34.070
The new world is calling

75
00:05:33.650 --> 00:05:36.450
See now look

76
00:05:36.030 --> 00:05:42.830
No matter how many seas separate us

77
00:05:42.500 --> 00:05:46.580
I’ve always got your back

78
00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:50.250
Don’t be afraid to advance

79
00:05:50.250 --> 00:05:52.620
Don’t forget

80
00:05:52.170 --> 00:05:54.010
We fight together

81
00:05:54.130 --> 00:06:01.930
I’ve never spoiled the memory

82
00:06:01.810 --> 00:06:04.640
Of the vast infinite sky,

83
00:06:04.270 --> 00:06:09.770
That I gazed upon that day

84
00:06:09.310 --> 00:06:13.240
We’ve come a long way

85
00:06:12.940 --> 00:06:17.140
Each with our own pledges in our hearts

86
00:06:16.700 --> 00:06:19.740
There is no doubt

87
00:06:19.320 --> 00:06:24.200
There are burdens we must bear

88
00:06:23.830 --> 00:06:26.710
The sun will rise

89
00:06:26.330 --> 00:06:31.630
And even illuminate our sorrows

90
00:06:31.300 --> 00:06:34.050
Yes, I believe it!

91
00:06:33.760 --> 00:06:40.470
One Piece will someday bind us together

92
00:06:40.100 --> 00:06:44.060
Let’s go and find it!

93
00:06:43.810 --> 00:06:47.850
You’re irreplaceable

94
00:06:48.150 --> 00:06:50.020
Don’t forget

95
00:06:49.900 --> 00:06:52.400
We fight together

96
00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:00.580
Let us turn back the clock once more...

97
00:07:00.580 --> 00:07:04.500
to the night when the Celestial Dragon's
ship docked in Goa Kingdom.

98
00:07:04.900 --> 00:07:11.740
<b>Will of the Winds</b>

99
00:07:05.810 --> 00:07:12.100
In a certain region of the East Blue,
in a small seaside village...

100
00:07:22.650 --> 00:07:25.860
Did you see the guy with
the huge face this afternoon?!

101
00:07:25.860 --> 00:07:28.090
Yeah! I've never seen anything like it!

102
00:07:28.090 --> 00:07:31.390
Look! His ship is huge too!

103
00:07:31.390 --> 00:07:33.830
Five hundred and eighty...

104
00:07:33.830 --> 00:07:35.830
Five hundred and eighty-one...

105
00:07:35.830 --> 00:07:38.600
Five hundred and eighty-two...

106
00:07:38.600 --> 00:07:40.940
Five hundred and eighty-three...

107
00:07:40.940 --> 00:07:42.980
Five hundred and eighty-four...

108
00:07:46.750 --> 00:07:49.000
You are late, Dragon!

109
00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:52.050
How long did you plan to make us vayyt?!

110
00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:54.550
Sorry.

111
00:07:55.790 --> 00:07:57.390
Vhaat did you...?!

112
00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:59.250
This is awful!

113
00:07:59.250 --> 00:08:01.400
Quickly! Get a doctor! It's an emergency!

114
00:08:01.400 --> 00:08:02.940
Roger!

115
00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:09.460
But really! Vherre have you been?!

116
00:08:09.460 --> 00:08:12.840
I was watching the world noble's
arrival ceremony.

117
00:08:14.660 --> 00:08:18.210
You vennt on your own viithout telling me?!

118
00:08:19.340 --> 00:08:22.680
If you were there, too, we would've
stuck out like sore thumbs.

119
00:08:24.470 --> 00:08:25.820
You mean... this...?!

120
00:08:28.050 --> 00:08:32.220
We must strive to grow
ever stronger, and with haste!

121
00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.730
How are our provisions?

122
00:08:35.390 --> 00:08:37.900
There was a village dojo that offered us food.

123
00:08:41.550 --> 00:08:43.260
Then we set sail!

124
00:08:43.260 --> 00:08:45.580
We will return to Baltigo!

125
00:08:51.740 --> 00:08:57.480
Some months later, the World Government having
concluded their inspection of the Kingdom of Goa...

126
00:09:01.870 --> 00:09:04.190
They've brought more trash!

127
00:09:05.590 --> 00:09:09.430
The people have settled
into their old routines...

128
00:09:10.370 --> 00:09:14.400
and the trash mountain has accumulated anew.

129
00:09:18.760 --> 00:09:22.170
Here I come, Ace!

130
00:09:22.680 --> 00:09:24.660
Gum-Gum...

131
00:09:25.340 --> 00:09:27.420
Pistol!

132
00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:43.660
What the hell was that? You call this a fight?

133
00:09:46.830 --> 00:09:51.000
You might pack a punch,
but what's the use if you miss every time?

134
00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:54.200
I told you, rubber really isn't suited for battle.

135
00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:55.840
Shut up! Don't say that!

136
00:09:56.160 --> 00:09:59.020
What?! I'm telling the truth!

137
00:09:59.020 --> 00:10:02.820
Sure, attacks bounce off you,
but you sink like a rock now!

138
00:10:02.820 --> 00:10:06.800
Stop making fun of the Gum-Gum Fruit!
I'll make you cry someday!

139
00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:09.520
I'm coming up with moves
even better than the pistol!

140
00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:12.390
Luffy, great work!

141
00:10:12.770 --> 00:10:16.460
Your arm stretched a lot farther
than it did yesterday!

142
00:10:16.760 --> 00:10:19.840
Sabo! You're too soft on Luffy!

143
00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:23.130
I knew I was stronger than yesterday!

144
00:10:23.130 --> 00:10:25.310
– Right, Sabo?!
– Right, Sabo?!

145
00:10:42.170 --> 00:10:45.080
Sabo was such a nice older brother...

146
00:10:45.080 --> 00:10:47.990
Say what?! You wish I'd died instead?!

147
00:10:56.020 --> 00:10:57.140
Ow. Huh?

148
00:11:07.830 --> 00:11:09.610
I've founded my own country.

149
00:11:10.390 --> 00:11:12.520
A country?

150
00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:15.720
What's this?

151
00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:18.860
Me too!

